pvardefs.name: pCallbackObj
pvardefs.desc: The instance that contains the callback method.

pvardefs.name: pCallbackName
pvardefs.desc: The name of the method that will be called when this request succeeds.

pvardefs.name: pResults
pvardefs.desc: The results returned from the HTTP request.

lvardefs.name: lvErrorCode
lvardefs.desc: An internal error code. Filled if something went wrong with the oSentryRequestWorker itself.

lvardefs.name: lvErrorInfo
lvardefs.desc: Internal error description. Filled if something went wrong with the oSentryRequestWorker itself.

lvardefs.name: lvHeaderText
lvardefs.desc: Can be filled with Sentry's response if Sentry rejects the request. Used for debugging purposes.

lvardefs.name: lvHttpStatusCode
lvardefs.desc: The HTTP status code returned by Sentry.

lvardefs.name: lvHttpStatusText
lvardefs.desc: The HTTP status text returned by Sentry.

lvardefs.name: lvResponseHeaders
lvardefs.desc: The headers of the response returned by Sentry. Contains an error message if applicable.
